    "name": "Black Zen White",
    "steam_appid": 3237030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black Zen White</strong> is a 2D puzzle platformer where the world flips  between two versions — black and white — each with different platforms, walls, and possibilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your mind, your timing, and help from unusual creatures to solve puzzles, unlock time-bending abilities, and reach the exit. Every level is a moment of calm — and cleverness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a contemplative, hand-drawn journey  inspired by East Asian art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/c0616d0f8bc507d8c68729d538f60c71.avif?t=1772290921\" alt=\"Game features\" width=780 height=66 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over <strong>100 levels</strong> for <strong>5 to 7 hours</strong> of playtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1 player</strong> and <strong>2 players co-op</strong> modes (with or without a controller!)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>12 hand-drawn landscapes</strong> (in 4K) in <strong>3 different environments</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 time-bending powers</strong> to unlock and <strong>10 different</strong> <strong>creatures</strong> to interact with</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Simple controls</strong> and <strong>realistic physics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of <strong>puzzles</strong> and a bit of <strong>timing</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>contemplative</strong> and <strong>relaxing</strong> atmosphere (most of the time) with a touch of silly humor</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/1dd123cb58b796c6eff72c15ff755779.avif?t=1772290921\" alt=\"Two colors. One path.\" width=780 height=66 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Jump, wait, land. What exists in black may vanish in white...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/9bc7968f93f80f6c0594775e2b15355d.poster.avif?t=1772290921\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/9bc7968f93f80f6c0594775e2b15355d.webm?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/945cc55c22879620610fee3e18421fad.avif?t=1772290921\" width=780 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Play alone or with a friend in co-op mode on the same computer or online with Steam Remote Play Together. Both players can play locally on the same keyboard. Only one player needs to own the game to play online co-op.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/5b2137192e34c1fb2d6deea5a78724ca.poster.avif?t=1772290921\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/5b2137192e34c1fb2d6deea5a78724ca.webm?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/5b2137192e34c1fb2d6deea5a78724ca.mp4?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/5e24619b8d911a47aac1b4e400c9ffc1.avif?t=1772290921\" alt=\"One puzzle. Many helpers.\" width=780 height=66 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Push friendly seals into place. Stack them, slide them, or give them a nudge — sometimes they help...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/36a5f784d1ca35210e9bcfb9ef59714e.poster.avif?t=1772290921\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/36a5f784d1ca35210e9bcfb9ef59714e.webm?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/5bfff369ebebbf11752467fe0a7db69b.avif?t=1772290921\" alt=\"One wall. Two realities.\" width=780 height=66 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Walk through what’s solid… or wait for it to disappear.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/b4f62cfdda0246d5d8a43606153aa503.poster.avif?t=1772290921\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/b4f62cfdda0246d5d8a43606153aa503.webm?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/4486f2a5d5567740e8313d2d696db493.avif?t=1772290921\" alt=\"Stay calm. Solve smart.\" width=780 height=66 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Zoom out, think through layers of shifting logic — black, then white, then black...</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/13e05923eadf27003437a6430cd999fb.poster.avif?t=1772290921\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/13e05923eadf27003437a6430cd999fb.webm?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/14aaa1eb2192a29033747f690bce9881.avif?t=1772290921\" alt=\"Patience is power. Bending time is power.\" width=780 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Slow down. Speed up. Master time itself to reach what was once unreachable.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/b02524446cc92f211fcd864f2298382b.poster.avif?t=1772290921\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/b02524446cc92f211fcd864f2298382b.webm?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/3ba6a4330dc12e37cc174a4fe46251da.avif?t=1772290921\" alt=\"The end remains. The way shifts.\" width=780 height=66 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>There’s always a way — if you wait, watch, and move with purpose.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/dc71eb9bdd1b937824f4a95b42ca6fa8.poster.avif?t=1772290921\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237030/extras/dc71eb9bdd1b937824f4a95b42ca6fa8.webm?t=1772290921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black Zen White</strong> invites you into a meditative world of duality, lighthearted logic, and surprising discoveries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>🖋️ Wishlist now and discover the power of stillness.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
